docs {
  Broadcasts a signed raw transaction to the Bitcoin network via a POST request with the hex in the request body.

  Parameters:
  1. body (string, required) - Hex-encoded raw transaction bytes as text/plain (max 8 MiB).

  Returns a result string containing the transaction ID of the broadcast transaction.

  Preferred over the GET variant for large transactions that would exceed URL length limits.
}
